	* Added: Users can identify themselves by username or email address when requesting a password reset
	* Changed: Use mailReceivers for mailings
	* Bugfix: Forgotten password didn't work

loginpage 1.2.0 - 2012-05-03
	* Adapted to core 2.2
	* Added: Cancel button in request forgotten password form to return to login

loginpage 1.1.4 - 2011-12-13
	* Added: CapsLock detection + warning
	* Added: Real names of demo-account persons
	* Added: Hook "loginpage.relogin.onreloginresponse"
	* Changed: Style of login-links to buttons to be easier recognized as clickable

